Hi Chris,

On Mon, Feb 04, 2002 at 11:53:14AM -0600, Chris Cleeland wrote:
> Does LocalObject ultimately inherit from Object.

Yes it does, which is why I've had problems with the multiple virtual
inheritance "diamond of death" in the past when trying to do "wicked"
cool optimizations for instantiations of local objects in the critical
path.

-Ossama
